Get a list of evidence items

getAllEvidenceItems.Rd

Retrieve all evidence items from the CIViC DB

getAllEvidenceItems(page = 1, count = 25)

Arguments

page

the page number to retrieve
count

the number of evidence items to retrieve

Value

An S3 Object of type civic_api containing the content, url, and response

Examples

getAllEvidenceItems(count = 10)
